title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Using flightplandatabase.com
description:
In this how to we are going to look how we can create a flight plan using flightplandatabase.com which can be used in MSFS 2020.

I will use both the quick method and the more advanced method to schedule a flight and we will look into the details of the flight plan and explain how they can be used for planning your flight.
